description: Astropulse: Reincarnation is a new single-player, sci-fi third-person shooter/RPG set on a war-torn future Earth. The game comes from Imagendary Studios and accomplished Blizzard artist Wei Wang.
title: Astropulse: Reincarnation Official Reveal Cinematic Trailer | Extended Version

description:
Introduced first in God of War in 2018 as a figure of legend, Týr’s role in the Norse saga evolved from myth to mentor in God of War Ragnarök: Valhalla.

Celebrate the sixth anniversary of God of War (2018) with the DLC Co-Directors Bruno Velazquez and Mihir Sheth as they share how Týr’s lore as a world traveler in the first game helped inspired his fighting styles.

#godofwar #tyr #gaming
title: God of War Ragnarök  Valhalla   Sparring with Týr   PS5 & PS4 Games
